sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as Sidecar Proxy<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Validator as AllowlistValidator<br/>(SSRF Protection)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller Pod<br/>Variable Port<br/>HTTP(S)
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP<br/>HTTP(S)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port=<host:port>
        Proxy->>Validator: Validate prefiller IP against allowlist
        Validator-->>Proxy: IP allowed (or SSRF disabled)

        Note over Proxy: Phase 1: Prefill Request<br/>Inject kv_transfer_params {do_remote_decode: true}<br/>Set max_tokens=1, disable streaming
        Proxy->>Prefiller: Modified completion request<br/>HTTP(S) / TLS 1.2+
        Prefiller-->>Proxy: Prefill response with<br/>kv_transfer_params (block IDs,<br/>engine ID, host, port)

        Note over Proxy: Phase 2: Decode Request<br/>Restore original streaming/token settings<br/>Inject prefiller's kv_transfer_params
        Proxy->>Decoder: Modified request with<br/>kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
        Decoder-->>Proxy: Decoded response (tokens)
        Proxy-->>Client: Final response<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefill Header)
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)
        Proxy->>Decoder: Passthrough request<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
        Decoder-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Validator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Maintenance (Background)
        Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CR<br/>HTTPS/443 (ServiceAccount token)
        K8sAPI-->>Validator: InferencePool with pod selectors
        Validator->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching selectors<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>Validator: Pod IPs for allowlist<br/>(30s resync period)
    end
